_components._string:
"Lucky elephant" is Special Lucky Draw Game which you can win grand car, up to 1,000,000 MB, up to 1,000,000 LAK u-money prizes and daily premium prizes.
How to earn turns
All u-money users are login the app everyday and share on Facebook for get free turns.
How to play game
    1. Earn turns to play game
    2. Choose game mode (Voice control - Speak 2 Jump or Manual control - Press 2 Jump)
    3. Level platforms are moving and if you choose "Speak 2 Jump" mode, make a noise or if "Press 2 Jump" mode, tap the button to make owl jump upwards to reach next level.
    4, Collect SIM boxes: "S1 – S2 – S3 – S4 – S5 – S6 – S7 – S8 – S9 – S10" to win amazing cars.
Maximum turn to play per day: 30 turns and all turns you get will be accumulated and can be used in the next day.
Free Daily turns
 -  Each u-money user will get one FREE turn everyday.
 -  Share to Facebook will get one FREE turn per day.
